#: index.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid "A quick explanation of the parts of the game screen."
msgstr "Hitra razlaga delov igralnega zaslona."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Screen"
msgstr "Igralni zaslon"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Game screen is in the center of the screen and is the largest section of "
"the window."
msgstr "Igralni zaslon je na sredini zaslona in je največji del okna."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid "Statusbar"
msgstr "Statusna vrstica"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Status bar is located at the bottom of the screen. It displays how many "
"pieces are left currently and the game timer, which keeps track of the "
"elapsed time from the start of the game until the game is finished."
msgstr ""
"Vrstica stanja se nahaja na dnu zaslona. Prikazuje, koliko kosov je trenutno "
"še ostalo, in časovnik igre, ki beleži pretečeni čas od začetka igre do "
"konca igre."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid "The KSame Mode"
msgstr "Način KSame"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:141
#, no-c-format
msgid "&klickety; provides a &ksame; scoring mode."
msgstr "&klickety; ponuja &ksame; način točkovanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:144
#, no-c-format
msgid "The score is calculated as follows:"
msgstr "Rezultat se izračuna na naslednji način:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:145
#, no-c-format
msgid "Subtract 2 from the number of marbles erased, and square the result."
msgstr "Odštejte 2 od števila izbrisanih frnikol in rezultat kvadrirajte."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As an example, if you erase 7 balls, then you get 25 points (7 minus 2 = 5, "
"5 squared is 25 points). If you erase 8 balls, then you get 36 points (8 "
"minus 2 = 6, 6 squared is 36 points)."
msgstr ""
"Na primer, če izbrišete 7 kroglic, dobite 25 točk (7 minus 2 = 5, 5 na "
"kvadrat je 25 točk). Če izbrišete 8 kroglic, dobite 36 točk (8 minus 2 = 6, "
"6 na kvadrat je 36 točk)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Get as many of the same pieces as you can, and then erase them in one click. "
"That way you will get a higher score. The game is over when there are no "
"pieces that can be erased."
msgstr ""
"Pridobite čim več enakih kosov in jih nato z enim klikom izbrišite. Tako "
"boste dosegli višjo oceno. Igre je konec, ko ni kosov, ki bi jih bilo mogoče "
"izbrisati."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:156
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The score will then be decreased according to the number of remaining "
"pieces. If you erase all pieces 1,000 bonus points will be added to the "
"final score."
msgstr ""
"Rezultat se bo nato zmanjšal glede na število preostalih kosov. Če izbrišete "
"vse figure, bo končnemu rezultatu dodanih 1.000 bonus točk."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid "A screenshot of &klickety; in KSame mode"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona &klickety; v načinu KSame"

