#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:356
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Redo</action> all undone moves."
msgstr "<action>Ponovi</action> vse razveljavljene poteze."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:360
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Difficulty</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Težavnost</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:365
#, no-c-format
msgid "Lets you set the difficulty level from a sub-menu."
msgstr "Omogoča nastavitev težavnostne stopnje iz podmenija."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:366
#, no-c-format
msgid "There are four levels of difficulty:"
msgstr "Obstajajo štiri težavnostne stopnje:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:368
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Very easy</guimenuitem>: 16 rows, 10 columns, 3 types of pieces."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Zelo enostavno</guimenuitem>: 16 vrstic, 10 stolpcev, 3 vrste "
"kosov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:369
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Easy</guimenuitem>: 16 rows, 10 columns, 4 types of pieces."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Enostavno</guimenuitem>: 16 vrstic, 10 stolpcev, 4 vrste kosov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:370
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Medium</guimenuitem>: 16 rows, 10 columns, 5 types of pieces."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Srednje</guimenuitem>: 16 vrstic, 10 stolpcev, 5 vrst kosov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:371
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Hard</guimenuitem>: 16 rows, 10 columns, 6 types of pieces."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Težko</guimenuitem>: 16 vrstic, 10 stolpcev, 6 vrst kosov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:374
#, no-c-format
msgid "There is also a <guimenuitem>Custom</guimenuitem> level settings."
msgstr "Obstajajo tudi nastavitve ravni <guimenuitem>Po meri</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:375
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you select <guimenuitem>Custom</guimenuitem>, then the settings you have "
"configured in the <guimenuitem>Configure - &klickety;</guimenuitem> dialog "
"will be used."
msgstr ""
"Če izberete <guimenuitem>Po meri</guimenuitem>, bodo uporabljene nastavitve, "
"ki ste jih konfigurirali v pogovornem oknu <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj - "
"&klickety;</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:382
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additionally &klickety; has the common &kde; <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> and "
"<guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu items, for more information read the sections "
"about the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings"
"\">Settings Menu</ulink> and <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus."
"html#menus-help\">Help Menu</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega &klickety; ima skupno &kde; Elementi menija <guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu> in <guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu>, za več informacij preberite razdelke o "
"<ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings\">meniju z "
"nastavitvami</ulink> in <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-help"
"\">meni Pomoč</ulink> v &kde; Osnove."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:393
#, no-c-format
msgid "Frequently asked questions"
msgstr "Pogosto zastavljena vprašanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:399
#, no-c-format
msgid "I want to change the way this game looks. Can I?"
msgstr "Želim spremeniti videz te igre. Ali lahko?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:400
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Yes. To change the way &klickety; looks use the menubar to open the <link "
"linkend=\"configuration\">configuration utility</link>."
msgstr ""
"Da Če želite spremeniti videz igre &klickety; uporabite menijsko vrstico, da "
"odprete <link linkend=\"configuration\">konfiguracijski pripomoček</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:403
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I use the keyboard to play the game?"
msgstr "Ali lahko uporabljam tipkovnico za igranje igre?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:404
#, no-c-format
msgid "No. This game does not feature a keyboard play mode yet."
msgstr "Ne. Ta igra še ne vsebuje načina igranja s tipkovnico."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:407
#, no-c-format
msgid "How to start the game in KSame mode?"
msgstr "Kako zagnati igro v načinu KSame?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:408
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can launch &klickety; with command <userinput>klickety --KSameMode</"
"userinput> or &ksame; menu entry in K menu."
msgstr ""
"Zaženete lahko &klickety; z ukazom <userinput>klickety --KSameMode</"
"userinput> ali &ksame; vnos menija v meniju K."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:415
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija igre"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:417
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure &klickety;…</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> opens the <guilabel>Configure - &klickety;</"
"guilabel> dialog."
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj &klickety;"
"…</guimenuitem></menuchoice> odpre pogovorno okno <guilabel>Konfiguriraj - "
"&klickety;</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:422
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>General options</title>"
msgstr "<title>Splošne možnosti</title>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:425
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show bound lines"
msgstr "Pokaži vezane črte"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:426
#, no-c-format
msgid "This option will show bound lines between pieces with different color."
msgstr "Ta možnost bo prikazala vezane črte med kosi različnih barv."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:431
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable animation"
msgstr "Omogoči animacijo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:432
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option will enable the falling and merging animation when pieces are "
"removed."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost bo omogočila animacijo padanja in združevanja, ko so deli "
"odstranjeni."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:437
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable highlight"
msgstr "Omogoči osvetlitev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:438
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option will enable highlighting on pieces hovered if they can be "
"removed."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost bo omogočila označevanje kosov, nad katerimi lebdite, če jih je "
"mogoče odstraniti."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:444
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>General options</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Splošne možnosti</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:447
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>General options</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Splošne možnosti</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:453
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Theme options</title>"
msgstr "<title>Možnosti teme</title>"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:456
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Theme</guilabel> selector"
msgstr "Izbirnik <guilabel>teme</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:457
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the <guilabel>Theme</guilabel> selector to set a theme for the game."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite izbirnik <guilabel>Tema</guilabel>, da nastavite temo za igro."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:461
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Theme options</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Možnosti teme</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:464
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Theme options</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Možnosti teme</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:470
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Background options</title>"
msgstr "<title>Možnosti ozadja</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:471
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can choose a background graphic for the game. There are three kinds of "
"background type you can use."
msgstr ""
"Za igro lahko izberete grafiko v ozadju. Uporabite lahko tri vrste ozadja."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:475
#, no-c-format
msgid "Theme"
msgstr "Tema"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:476
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use the background shipped with the current theme."
msgstr "Uporabite ozadje, poslano s trenutno temo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:479
#, no-c-format
msgid "Color"
msgstr "Barva"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:480
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use a custom solid color for the background."
msgstr "Za ozadje uporabite enobarvno barvo po meri."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:483
#, no-c-format
msgid "Image"
msgstr "Slika"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:484
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use an image for the background graphic."
msgstr "Za grafiko v ozadju uporabite sliko."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:489
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Background options</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Možnosti ozadja</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:492
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Background options</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Možnosti ozadja</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:498
#, no-c-format
msgid "Custom Game options"
msgstr "Možnosti igre po meri"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:499
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can set the <guilabel>Height:</guilabel> and <guilabel>Width:</guilabel> "
"of the board and the <guilabel>Color count:</guilabel> used in your custom "
"level."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite lahko <guilabel>Višino:</guilabel> in <guilabel>Širino:</guilabel> "
"plošče ter <guilabel>Število barv:</guilabel>, uporabljeno na ravni po meri."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:504
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Custom game options</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Možnosti igre po meri</screeninfo>"

